Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.41,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0015,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had all that done to you and\Nyou act like nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Keep looking down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, after we've gotten\Nrid of your sword-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and if we have trouble\Nfinding a buyer for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have fun with this\Npervert I know, shooting drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from dawn till dusk every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy can't get a hard-on\Nunless it's hardcore S&M.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:02:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have him get you hooked on drugs,\Nshake your ass, and eat his shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm sure you'll\Nsee things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the video comes out,\NI'll be sure to buy a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass. You can't win\Nthat much with Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You wanna fight? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, any of you got Zippo oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the guy who pulled off\Na robbery at Shin-Okubo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the news about the Iranian...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being chased by a guy with\Nknife in hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well there's a warrant out\Nfor the guy's arrest, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NKeep it down over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you really did show up.\NI don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my dear Revy,\Nwhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did wanna fuck, eh? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin. Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really gone\Noverboard this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna see\Nmy sword that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all make the\Nmarch to hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill 'em all, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look at this!\NI've never seen such a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys! Don't hide!\NShow some balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing! I'd better get\Nserious or I could be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuki! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Try catching up with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ow! Ow!\N- Amazing! That woman's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have the chance\Nto do it with her in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better prepare the stage\Nif I'm gonna do this right! Right, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I give up! I really give up!\NI give! Give! You know, give, give, give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give? Give me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I cannot speak... ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna give me\Nsomething, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come on, what the fuck\Nare you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, give up, so give!\NSeriously! I give, give! Give!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yapping, you goofball.\NYou gonna give it to me or not? C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jumbo! The game's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy we made a mess, all we got\Nleft is to mop up the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look for\Nour princess and that sack o' shit.
