Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go around the corridor\Nand meet at the pool, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see Rock, bring him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky,\Nhe may be with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\NI'm counting on you, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stubborn guy.\NLet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've run outta luck.\NI pity you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's getting outta here alive.\NNot a single one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hell's Motel.\NRun away, if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the boogeyman's\Ngonna eat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to live forever, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything.\NMr. Chaka, have the other guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mr. Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you! Shut up. What was that?\NI'd say they're probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, you bastard?!\NHow can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of following you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got time to bitch,\Ngo look for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?\NThe plan's screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're running from me?\NFine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shot your own subordinates.\NI've never seen such despicable scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that you're\Nstill running around...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I guess you haven't met up\Nwith Jumbo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who cares?\NI've been wanting to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met\Na female gunman before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opportunity has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep with me, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ha, yeah. So that's it.\NWhat a joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:08:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment this can hits the\Nfloor is our signal, kitty-cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, nine, eight, seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to challenge me as\Na gunman? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to duel against a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...below-third-rate sack o' shit\Nlike you, punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a desire to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're happy to die,\Nthen it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Jumbo finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you. Stop, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sack o' shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Jumbo.\NI brought you your prom date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny.\NYou get on my nerves, sword man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss isn't here any more.\NBecause I shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're done here, right?\NI suggest...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you go home and cook\Nsome octopus dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a pathetic\Nlittle dog like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would ever drop your own\Nwallet with cash in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right then, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, show me how good you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw in any manner you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I'll kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Revy and Gin are\Ngetting their job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay here a little longer,\Njust in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave you alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I found out that you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being dragged into this\Nincident, our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. You just said that\NI was being dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken, Mr. Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm the person at\Nthe core of this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... you are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again. You are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yukio! What are you saying?\N- Mr. Okajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have accepted the position of\Nfourteenth Washimine Clan deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right now I hold the highest rank\Nwithin the Washimine Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wasn't dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am at the core of it all.\NAnd you are... my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew what kind of world this is,\Nand yet you stepped in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're filled with evil and\Ndon't have a shred of decency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world where people like\Nthat betray and kill one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima. I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just watch you\Nget dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't just watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Mr. Bando's\Ncause of death was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your clan's\Nlost its driving force...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the parent clan is\Nneglecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's necessary to stand\Nup against a stronger power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose you're the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who can save the clan from\Nthat predicament. Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To renew the brotherhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only someone from the direct bloodline\Nwill be recognized as a successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say it. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old tradition that\Nno one's bothered to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how\Nridiculous it sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we only know how to live\Nwithin those guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the order we abide by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what happens to your life?\NNobody wanted this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Mr. Bando,\Nnot Mr. Gin, and not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was desperate to keep you\Naway from the fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were keeping you from\Nstanding here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been standing here sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this would not have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's the Kousa Clan\Nwho is to be blamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are... You are forcefully trying\Nto bear this burden by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what we\Ntalked about at the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are like dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A certain Frenchman said{\i0}\N{\i1}that people are like dice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You throw yourself in the{\i0}\N{\i1}direction of your choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't forced. I chose this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing all I can for my father\Nand the people who loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose sight of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll be forced to live with a burden\Nthat you don't have to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You are in the twilight.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say these things because\Nyou've stayed in the twilight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot have resolve unless\NI believe that I chose this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone's life, honor,\Nand future depends on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do\Nbut fight for them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like tonight! If I didn't believe\Nthat I had chosen this responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't have endured\Nwhat I went through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I believed in God...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...right up to the day cops beat the hell{\i0}\N{\i1}outta me for something I didn't do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the next time you try telling{\i0}\N{\i1}me what's proper...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you'll no longer be one of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing's changed since then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the midst of this night{\i0}\N{\i1}that she has experienced...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I am completely powerless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no words to give this{\i0}\N{\i1}girl before me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who's stumbling{\i0}\N{\i1}towards your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am where I'm standing.{\i0}\N{\i1}Nowhere else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a lie.{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm not standing anywhere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too easy a way for you to die,\Nbut the style suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that it would be acceptable\Nfor me to carry it all on my shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if it means\Nsaving Gin and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yukio, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima. Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you try to\Nmake a stand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...understand what you were\Ntalking to me about in the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I can say\Nthis clearly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you\Nsubmerged yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the southeast Asian\Nunderworld is possibly because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were seeking something different\Nfrom Japan. Different from your daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end,\Nyou haven't chosen anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not returning to your\Ncasual life under the sun yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...refuse to sink further into\Ndarkness where the evil roams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just remain\Nstanding where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it earlier,\Nthat you wanted to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then save me!\NSave the Washimine Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Gin, the members, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can. Because you\Ndon't actually want to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to lose that normal\Nlife that you thought you threw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sit back and watch me die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you lose the very last of\Nyour recollections of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't want to lose anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have yearnings for\Nthat which you've thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could you possibly protect,\Nfeeling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you like that, who could\Nyou possibly save?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be in\Nthe same place as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a guy who chose\Nnot to live a life of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. But I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but be upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet, baby. You cut the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show that to me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being short tempered\Nwon't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you and the interpreter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to waste that.\NIf you're lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, if you're unlucky, there will\Nbe other opportunities for us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for tonight.\NBut I pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pray we never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock still hasn't\Nreturned to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he be\Nwasting his time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as well. There's nothing\Nfor him to do for a while anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assault on the Washimine\NGroup will begin at 0750 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Form two squads to go in and\Ndestroy their headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...offices and all confirmed hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack team\Nhas already moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall destroy all of the Washimine\Nforces thoroughly and immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach these Japanese the\Netiquette of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you should not wish for the\Nsame way of life as his.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
